properties.text:
Resolution Calculator Example

This node calculates upscaled dimensions from:
- IMAGE tensors (connect from image loaders)
- LATENT tensors (connect from VAE encode/generation)

Use cases:
- Calculate target dimensions for upscalers
- Plan memory usage for large generations
- Ensure dimensions are divisible by 8

Scale factors optimized for SDXL and FLUX models.
